entry.description:
Commands to assist the reuse of boxes (set up by \sbox or
by the lrbox environment); the \settobox...
commands behave similarly to the \settowidth (etc.)
commands.  For example:

  \newsavebox{\mybox}
  \newlength{\mylength}
  \sbox{\mybox}{Hello World}
  \settoboxwidth{\mylength}{\mybox}



The package is part of the oberdiek bundle.
